metadata.title: Careful | Gurleen Pannu | Standup Comedy
metadata.description:
MY AUS-NZ & INDIA TOUR IS LIVE!  
TICKETS HERE : https://linktr.ee/pannugurleen

I'm excited to present another  #StandUpComedy video on Youtube! Haan aa gaya yaad password…
My name is Gurleen Pannu, join me as I share my experience about travelling & being overly cautious about safety. Just a small bit about me and my brother exploring Delhi anxiously.  Delhi was my first ever city where I lived alone  so it  will always be very close to my heart. Share the video with your friends & family.
DO
